graphiti-falkordb-stack
Copyright 2026 Xindong

This product contains modifications to graphiti-core (Apache-2.0,
https://github.com/getzep/graphiti). The modifications are applied at
container build time via the Python patch scripts in
docker/graphiti-ark/, and are described in PATCHES.md.

The unmodified upstream falkordb/falkordb-server and
falkordb/falkordb-browser images are used as runtime dependencies and
are not modified by this project.
